00:00:01.884 --> 00:00:03.539
I feel like
I'm in a dream.

2
00:00:06.789 --> 00:00:09.563
Welcome to the White Lotus
in Sicily!

3
00:00:09.648 --> 00:00:11.985
It's very intoxicating.

4
00:00:18.155 --> 00:00:22.109
<i>♪ Oh ♪</i>

5
00:00:24.906 --> 00:00:26.493
I'm very attracted to you.

6
00:00:26.578 --> 00:00:28.429
Would you be interested
in having an affair?

7
00:00:35.789 --> 00:00:37.890
Epic theme playing...

8
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:45.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
